item.title: Help please when i type the server in it says it isint on
item.dc:creator: @dragonblood_dan dragonblood_dan
item.description:
@dragonblood_dan wrote:

well maybe he has different comps? when you change the IP of the server by going file>new server in moparscape you may need to change the port aswell by going File>New Port.
try the following ports:
43594
5555
if these don’t work contact the server owner/host and ask them the port. also the server may be connected through hamachi, if you have previously used hamachio to connect to this network make sure hamachi is still on now, and makesure the hamachi network name is white in the hamachi window, if it is not white double click the name of the server to connect to it in hamachi.
